text: Anapausa longipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1966. It is known from New Guinea.BioLib.cz - Anapausa longipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1966
title: Anapausa longipennis
